## Backend API Reference (Sudah Ada)

### Hardware Installation (via Ticketing)
```
GET  /tickets/paginated?category=HARDWARE_INSTALLATION  → PaginatedResponse<Ticket>
GET  /tickets/:id                                        → Ticket detail
PATCH /tickets/:id/status                                → Update status
```

### ICT Budget
```
GET   /ict-budget           → IctBudgetRequest[]
GET   /ict-budget/:id       → IctBudgetRequest
PATCH /ict-budget/:id/status → { status: IctBudgetRealizationStatus }
```
**Status enum**: `FORM_PENDING → FORM_DOWNLOADED → FORM_UPLOADED → PENDING → APPROVED → PURCHASING → ARRIVED → REALIZED | REJECTED`

### Installation Schedule
```
GET   /installation-schedule                    → InstallationSchedule[]
GET   /installation-schedule/available-slots?date=YYYY-MM-DD → slot availability
POST  /installation-schedule                    → Create schedule
PATCH /installation-schedule/:id/approve        → Approve schedule
PATCH /installation-schedule/:id/complete       → Complete schedule
```

### Access Request
```
GET   /access-request           → AccessRequest[]
GET   /access-request/:id       → AccessRequest
PATCH /access-request/:id/verify   → Verify
PATCH /access-request/:id/approve  → Approve
PATCH /access-request/:id/create-access → Create credentials
PATCH /access-request/:id/reject   → Reject
```
**Status enum**: `PENDING → VERIFIED → APPROVED → ACCESS_CREATED | REJECTED`

### Lost Item
```
GET   /lost-item           → LostItemReport[]
GET   /lost-item/:id       → LostItemReport
PATCH /lost-item/:id/status → { status: LostItemStatus }
```
**Status enum**: `REPORTED → FOUND | LOST`

