## Design Principles (NON-NEGOTIABLE)

| Rule | Detail |
|------|--------|
| **Reuse existing components** | `StatsCard`, `Badge`, `Select`, `AnimatedNumber`, `UserAvatar`, `ModernCalendar` |
| **HSL CSS Variables** | Gunakan `hsl(var(--primary))`, `hsl(var(--card))`, `hsl(var(--border))` — BUKAN `bg-white` atau `bg-slate-800` langsung |
| **Animations** | `animate-fade-in-up`, `stagger-1/2/3` classes |
| **Rounded corners** | `rounded-xl` untuk komponen kecil, `rounded-2xl` untuk panel besar |
| **Font weights** | Title: `font-extrabold`, Labels: `font-semibold`, Body: `font-medium` |
| **NO mock data** | Semua data dari API real. Jika API belum ada, tampilkan empty state yang proper |
| **Drawer pattern** | `framer-motion` slide-in drawer untuk detail, actions terhubung ke mutation hooks |
| **Consistent header** | Icon container (12x12 rounded-xl) + title (3xl extrabold) + subtitle + action buttons |

